'''''Decisive Battles of the American Civil War, Vol. 2''''' is a 1988 [[computer wargame]] developed and published by [[Strategic Studies Group]].

==Gameplay==
''Decisive Battles of the American Civil War, Vol. 2'' is a game in which five [[American Civil War]] battles that took place from the middle of 1862 through the end of 1863 are simulated.<ref name="CGW54"/>

